# [M] Gravy

- Oil | 1.5 tbspn | 
- Flour | 1.5 tbsn | 
- Water | 1 cup | 

## Instructions

Add flour to 3/4 cup of water. Stir vigorously. (This prevents clumping)

Heat oil to med

Slowly add water/flour

Reduce heat to low

Use up to 1/4 cup water to wash flour out of container, looking at thickness
